description:
finally!!! after 3 years, the last game in this series. if you've played all of them by now, thank you for your patience and your faith in me. 

all my games are free, but if you would like to contribute anything,  donate it to  my friend's rent and expenses  fund!

CW: some discussion of systemic racism & colonialism, HRT, distorted thoughts. brief mentions: food insecurity, assault by a doctor, alcohol
